{"tid":1101452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[會窮]女大生拍賣處女16萬　60男人排隊報名","createTime":"2019-04-11T04:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T06:40:48.000Z","uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"75acb94acfc5ebb72f2f894703d9a75fb4903a88","tid":1101452,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:51:02.000Z","msg":"哈薩克一名19歲女大生札妮貝可娃(Aynur Zhanibekova)，最近上一個談話性節目，更大膽地宣示要拍賣自己的處女，為自己賺取學費，減輕媽媽的負擔。節目結束後，吸引60名男子排隊報名。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，札妮貝可娃最近上《Oz oyym》節目，她說她看到許多同學朋友交了男朋友後，進行「免費」做愛，她說：「我為什麼要免費做愛，我覺得我可以利用做愛來賺錢。」、「我需要錢來付學費。」札妮貝可娃說，她的媽媽努力工作，但是仍然沒有多餘的錢可以負擔學費，「我想要幫忙我媽」。因此札妮貝可娃開價200萬哈薩克幣(約新台幣16萬元)，要拍賣自己的處女。<br />\n<br />\n札妮貝可娃表示，她希望利用這一筆錢，一方面付學費，二來能進行處女膜重建手術，多餘的錢還能去美容院。節目結束後，竟然吸引了60名男子排隊報名，札妮貝可娃就在考慮想提高價碼。<br />\n<br />\n不過札妮貝可娃的決定，也引來不少民眾批評，有觀眾就說：「太下流了，真為她的父母感到羞愧。」、「可恥！」但也有觀眾支持她，說：「這是她的身體，她有權如何使用她的身體。」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190411/640_ab2298a3efabc77c2e66080e3c01f42e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190411%2F640_ab2298a3efabc77c2e66080e3c01f42e.jpg&h=d57d9b3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dc2a4667a7060a4aeda15aef55f4dd587f329e8","tid":1101452,"uid":165510,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:52:15.000Z","msg":"咁都有60個人排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係有窿就大曬"},{"pid":"43292a0f566c611fd52c0d617acc8b4fe156804d","tid":1101452,"uid":67346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:52:33.000Z","msg":"嗰60個男人擔唔擔心有三高<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3985550318e1668b5ad10b6d0bdc334783b2559","tid":1101452,"uid":58335,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:52:39.000Z","msg":"佢比返16萬個男人？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c50a67d01092988b09912ba0c453bc8b7c438f","tid":1101452,"uid":208553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:53:28.000Z","msg":"身體自主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7221bfd8b7534dfc110ef399a755970f1003fa","tid":1101452,"uid":46910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔撚係掛"},{"pid":"f01630393844294a1ba1cce9b302a548a4b50fb5","tid":1101452,"uid":193131,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:53:54.000Z","msg":"就係佢咁的樣，啲人先相信係真的處女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c0996215951d01ffbcec1feb5edfb8023c0c25","tid":1101452,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:54:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d176af353a99ae1442ab36b222b4b2d25aa812","tid":1101452,"uid":111571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:55:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3bcf0f9054d8441d37bedb34df7bbae4d483aca4","tid":1101452,"uid":9726,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:56:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6ff62a9084f60d6f50c74ed6d65519a48f2a531","tid":1101452,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:56:04.000Z","msg":"拍賣處男揮手區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bf393aba8058f886675ed8e3536337e0ebf3d6","tid":1101452,"uid":170009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:56:45.000Z","msg":"賣完再重建再賣 發達大計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touc